white-flippered penguin
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a subspecies of the little blue penguin, found on Banks Peninsular and Motunau Island
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:Environment
Region:[none]
See:little blue penguin
Pronunciation:
Notes: <i>Eudyptula minor albosignata</i> also silver penguin
